.SH EXAMPLES
.SS Inspecting the returned CSSTransition
The transition in the following example changes the width of the box on
hover.
Calling \f[CR]Element.getAnimations()\f[R] returns an array of all
\f[CR]Animation\f[R] objects.
In our case this returns a \f[CR]CSSTransition\f[R] object, representing
the animation created.
